Package: autotextclassifier
Title: R package for automatically classifying texts based on tidymodels
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Jae Yeon",
           family = "Kim",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jaeyeonkim@berkeley.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6533-7910")),
      person(given = "Milan",
           family = "de Vries",
           role = c("aut"),
           email = "milandv@jhu.edu"))
Description: This package automatically classifies texts based on a binary category using lasso, random forest, and XGboost algorithms. The package is built on the tidymodels framework.
Maintainer: Jae Yeon Kim <jaeyeonkim@berkeley.edu>
